The paper proposes a novel recommendation model that utilizes latent factor and word embedding models. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories, including Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), and Computation and Language (cs.CL). However, since the focus is on recommendation, cs.IR and cs.LG are the most likely sub-categories.
